         <note>EPISODIO HISTÓRICO DE LA GUERRA DE LA INDEPENDENCIA</note>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="1"> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="iñche" pos="PN" corresp="I/me"><m baseForm="iñche" type="1s">Inche</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="my"><m baseForm="ñi" type="1s">ni</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="l'aku" pos="N" corresp="(paternal) grandfather/grandchild"><m baseForm="l'aku" type="root" corresp="(paternal) grandfather/grandchild">láku</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="mongen" pos="V" corresp="live/be healthy"><m baseForm="monge" type="root" corresp="live/be healthy">moŋe</m><m baseForm="fu" type="bi">fú</m><m baseForm="iy" type="ind3">i</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="kuyfi" pos="AV" corresp="long time"><m baseForm="kuyfi" type="root" corresp="long time">kúifi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="antü" pos="N" corresp="day/sun"><m baseForm="antü" type="root" corresp="day/sun">ántə</m></w>. <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="Juan" pos="NP" corresp="Juan">Juan</w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="José" pos="NP" corresp="José">José</w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="Kintuprai" pos="NP" corresp="Kintuprai">Kintuprai</w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pin" pos="V" corresp="say"><m baseForm="pi" type="root" corresp="say">pi</m><m baseForm="nge" type="pass">ŋe</m><m baseForm="fu" type="bi">fu</m><m baseForm="iy" type="ind3s"></m></w>-<w xml:lang="arn" lemma="iñche" pos="PN" corresp="I/me"><m baseForm="iñche" type="1s">inche</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="l'aku" pos="N" corresp="(paternal) grandfather/grandchild"><m baseForm="l'aku" type="root" corresp="(paternal) grandfather/grandchild">laku</m></w>; pichü <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="müt'en" pos="AV" corresp="merely/only"><m baseForm="müt'e" type="root" corresp="very/much">məte</m><m baseForm="(ü)n" type="nmlz">n</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="kimün" pos="V" corresp="know"><m baseForm="kim" type="root" corresp="know">kim</m><m baseForm="pa" type="cis">pa</m><m baseForm="fi" type="3dir">fí</m><m baseForm="(ü)n" type="ind1s">n</m></w>.</p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="2"> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="feychi" pos="D"><m baseForm="fey" type="D">Fei</m><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">ti</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="rupan" pos="V" corresp="pass"><m baseForm="rupa" type="root" corresp="pass">rupa</m><m baseForm="iy" type="ind3">i</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="weichan" pos="N" corresp="war/battle"><m baseForm="weicha" type="root" corresp="fight">weicha</m><m baseForm="(ü)n" type="nmlz">n</m></w>-<w xml:lang="arn" lemma="mew" pos="P"><m baseForm="mew" type="P">mo</m></w>. <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="kombidan" pos="V" corresp="share/invite" source="sp:convidar"><m baseForm="kombidan" type="root" corresp="share/invite">Kombídan</m><m baseForm="nge" type="pass">ŋe</m><m baseForm="iy" type="ind3">i</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="kasike" pos="N" corresp="chieftain" source="sp:casique"><m baseForm="kasike" type="root" corresp="chieftain">kasike</m></w>; <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="düngun" pos="N" corresp="thing/news/word/thought"><m baseForm="düngu" type="root" corresp="thing/news/word/thought">züŋu</m><m baseForm="eyeu" type="indinv3-3">eu</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="kawallero" pos="N" corresp="gentleman" source="sp:caballero"><m baseForm="kawallero" type="root" corresp="gentleman">kawaʎero</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="nielu" pos="N" corresp="having"><m baseForm="nie" type="root" corresp="have">nie</m><m baseForm="lu" type="svn">l’u</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ta" pos="DA"><m baseForm="ta" type="DA">ta</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="weichan" pos="N" corresp="war/battle"><m baseForm="weicha" type="root" corresp="fight">weicha</m><m baseForm="(ü)n" type="nmlz">n</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="awkandüngu" pos="CN" corresp="words of uprising"><m baseForm="awkan" type="root" corresp="wild/rebellious">aukan</m><m baseForm="düngu" type="root" corresp="thing/news/word/thought">züŋu</m></w>: </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="3"> “Kəpape <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> señor kasike; l’eukeano ni <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> señor kasike. </p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="4"> —Petu ŋai ayüŋeñi l’aŋmŋeia, moŋko <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona eŋn. L’eukeyano ni <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> señor kasike, niei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ta" pos="DA"><m baseForm="ta" type="DA">ta</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> kəme ke kona, kumpañaianno <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> weichan-mo”. </p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="5"> —Məlei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ta" pos="DA"><m baseForm="ta" type="DA">ta</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona ka; kumpañafin <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> tañi señor koronel. N̰əl’eman <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona; məlei tañi kapitanejo, məlei tañi sárjentu, məlei tañi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> fiskal, kəme ke went’u. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="6"> Zeuma <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> l’eumefin tañi señor koronel; fei t’okilantə kənol’ano <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor koronel; t’okilántəmo moŋko nian ni <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona. Pel’i züŋu t’uftulen, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor koronel.</p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="7"> —T’uyun <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> mi kumpañayateu, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señór kasike. —Zeuma <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> fil’ moŋko t’uftunməlei ni <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="8"> Chi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kasike yei ni <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> weichan-mo; kewálu yei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> kapitanejo, yei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> sárjento, yei ni <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> fískal, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kásike, meli kasike. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="9"> Feimo yei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> rul’pazüŋualu, amoi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> laku Juan José Kintuprai; kimí <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> winkanət’am; yei ni rulpazüŋualu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kasike; amoi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> Juan José Kintuprai, feimai s’ul’pazüŋupailu. </p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="10"> Maipue piŋei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> mapu; məlei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> kiñe l’eufu; feichi nome l’eufu ml’eu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> weichan. Feimu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> laŋəmuiŋn, kewaiŋn, aldü <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> lai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> winka. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="11"> Feimu afi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> weichan; femŋechi alküpan fachi nət’ám, feimu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> nü´t’amkan <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="iñche" pos="PN" corresp="I/me"><m baseForm="iñche" type="1s">inche</m></w> eimi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> went’u-mo. Alküŋi, peuwü´l’u <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> went’u nü´t’amkakai. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="12"> —Fiskal, wes’küyaimi; amoaimi señor koronel-mo; fei piafimi: “Zeuma <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> nákəmi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> kewán, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor koronel. Ásta famo mten kumpañafin <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor koronel. Ni <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona niewelai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> moŋam”, fei pifiŋe <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor kóronel. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="13"> Niefuli <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> moŋam ni <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona kumpañañiekayaufin <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor koronel, amolafun. Apüme <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> z’ókin, niewelai ni moŋam ni <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona. Wes’küéno <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor kásike: “asta famo mten kumpañafin” pi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> ni señor kasike, señor koronel. </p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="14"> —Muchas gracias <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor kasike; amotupe ni señor kasike; fei piafimi mai: “¡Chiʎaka-weʎuŋn pe <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona!”</p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="15"> —¡Kápitanejo, sárjento, pú viskal, chiʎakaweʎu pe! Amotuyen mapu-mo; petuyen rüpü, yen amotuam. Küme pel’üyen mai, wewi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> kewan <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor koronel. Elutueyen rüpü <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor koro- nel. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="16"> ¡Hîa! ¡amóyen <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona! ¡Sîha! t’üftui <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona. Pra kaweʎuiŋn; feimu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> ¡viva! rüpüiŋn, ¡vivai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> señor koronel! </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="17"> Wenu kaweʎu məleiŋn, moŋko <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kasike wenu kaweʎu; prakaweʎuleiŋn; feimu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> ¡vívai! təfi eŋn moŋko <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> che. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="18"> Lalai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> moŋko tvichi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> kona; kiñe ke mten t’ipai alfün. <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="iñche" pos="PN" corresp="I/me"><m baseForm="iñche" type="1s">Inche</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> laku eputue wesoi machetaso sable; <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> foru loŋko wampu naqi, prapalai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> vos’u yom. Femŋen l’ai. </p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="19"> Moŋko akutui <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> mapu-mo. T’uyukechi moŋko <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> fücha, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> t'emche. N̰emai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> t’emche, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> füt'a akutulmo. </p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="20"> N̰ələmúiŋn, pətúiŋn, laŋmi kuʎ’in, kəmé ke waka il’óiŋn, laŋmiŋn. T’uyunkechi, t’uyúiŋn, siempre ŋemaiŋn.</p>

         <note>LA ERUPCIÓN DEL VOLCÁN CALBUCO</note>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="1"> Kiñe kəme züŋun, maziao kəme, züŋuukiyu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> kaweʎeru eyu. Feimo nüt’amkaeno: </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="2"> Petu üyi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> pis’e l’il’; fit’ui maziao, kensabe chuŋaiel moŋen. Maziao afkətulŋi; femŋemalai z’ume fenten t’ipantu moŋien; al’külafien, al’küúnmalafien. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="3"> Feimo <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> al’kufien; kəpaichi akuichi züŋu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> femŋen, petu úyen <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> pis’e <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> kordiʎera, kəme al’kufiyen. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="4"> Akúi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> fitun Osorno; <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> tapü mamel’ l’iqz’úi, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> tue moŋko l’iqs’úi. </p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="5"> Feimo maziao afkütúi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> moŋen. Kensabe weza zuŋu məlai, ŋepai. Ul’kupei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> chao dioz. Kishu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> chao dioz t’okiai. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="6"> Feimo fi pifuyen: “Kachu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> peueláyen, l’aqai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> yen kuʎin moŋko; kensabe fünlayen ket’an, yen təkun. Chumŋéchi moŋəfuien, ŋepáyi fünnofule in ket’an”. </p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="7"> Moŋkoi maziaoi qüyí <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> l’il’; ¿chen kensabe qüikepi mino? Məlepai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> kensabe kuyul’kuz'a. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="8"> Petui kai təfichi l’il’; cheu qüyí <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> l’il’ məlewelai, l’ófi. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="9"> Fei pi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> aleman fei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> nüt’amo: “Wel’u zuaml’aimn; inchen mapu-mo qüiki l’il’. Feimo kimiefiyen”. </p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="10"> Feimo t’epeukəlayen, pieyenmo <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> aleman. Feimo kiñe no zuamiyen. </p>


         <note>LA LLEGADA DEL FORASTERO</note>
         <p xml:lang="arn">Akui <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> wüt’an kiñe s’uka-mo; wankai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> t’ewa; t’ipapai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> ŋen s’uka; pichi all’ü <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> məlei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chi" pos="DA"><m baseForm="chi" type="DA">chi</m></w> ŋen s’uka: </p>
         <p xml:lang="arn"> —T’ekanaŋe, al’kütuŋe, puturupaŋe; famo chaku mlei; anüpaŋe. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="Dueño:"> Marimari, winkâu; ¿kəme moŋeimí? </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="Forastero:"> Mai; kəme moŋenkâ. ¿Eimi kəme moŋeimi? </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="D."> —Kəme moŋenkâ. ¿Kulai akuimi, akun məl’el’kelafúimi? </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="F."> —Pichi kulai məten akun, l’oftunieimi, t’ekanaqlepan tami ruka-mo. ¿Chenzuŋu nielaimi təfâ, ŋen rukâ?</p>


         <p xml:lang="arn" n="D."> —Nielan chenzuŋu; kəme <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> məlen. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="F."> —Fei üs’kemai, tami kəme ml’es’ken; tüyün <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> tami kü´me ml’es’kel’mo. ¿Kəme məlei mi kumpan, tami malqen, mi <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pu" pos="PL"><m baseForm="pu" type="PL">pu</m></w> vochü´m, nawe kai? </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="D."> —Məlekéi, fil’ kəmeli təva. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="F."> —Kəmes’ki mai. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="D."> —¿Kintukəpaimi? </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="F."> —Pichi ke zuamŋen; kintukəpan; welu mi peniefiel, entuan <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> zuam. </p>

         <note>CANTO DEL BORRACHO</note>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Moʎipülkün; winka pülkün kəmei. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Yu wenüi winkâ. <lb/> Fei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> freneno kiñe chas’u, <lb/> feimo <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> moʎi pülkü. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Kəmei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> ni wenüi winkâ, fei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> freneno. <lb/> Feimo ŋoʎi-pülkün, <lb/> kiñe chas’u, kiñe fül’. <lb/> Amoyu mai, chachan, <lb/> ŋoʎi pülkün mai, chachan, <lb/> winka pülkü-mo. <lb/> Kəmei <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="may" pos="AV" corresp="yes/indeed"><m baseForm="may" corresp="yes/indeed">mai</m></w> wenüi winka. </p>

